<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Cafe Aroma - B</title>
<style>
body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    background-color: #fdf6f0;
    color: #333;
}
header {
    background-color: #b5651d;
    color: white;
    padding: 20px 0;
    text-align: center;
}
nav {
    background-color: #8b4513;
}
nav ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 10px 0;
}
nav ul li {
    margin: 0 20px;
}
nav ul li a {
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
}
.hero {
    background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509042239860-f550ce710b93?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    height: 400px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
}
main {
    padding: 40px 20px;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: auto;
}
footer {
    background-color: #8b4513;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px 0;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
<h1>Cafe Aroma</h1>
</header>

<nav>
<ul>
<li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
<li><a href="#">Menu</a></li>
<li><a href="#">About</a></li>
</ul>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
<h2 style="font-family:'Courier New', monospace; color:#00FFFF;">
Fresh Coffee - Folder 2 (Server 1)
</h2>
</div>

<main>
<h3>Our Special Menu</h3>
<p>Espresso - $3</p>
<p>Cappuccino - $4</p>
<p>Latte - $4.5</p>

<h3>About Us</h3>
<p>Welcome to Cafe Aroma! Unique code: <strong>ALB-F2-S1</strong></p>
</main>

<footer>
© 2026 Cafe Aroma
</footer>

</body>
</html>
